def creation_dataset(dataset, time_step=1):
    dataX = np.array([dataset[i:i+time_step, 0] for i in range(len(dataset)-time_step-1)])
    dataY = np.array([dataset[i+time_step, 0] for i in range(len(dataset)-time_step-1)])
    return dataX, dataY

        lst_output.append(yhat.tolist()[0])

Support Vector Machine¶

kernel= "linear"¶

In [19]:
#Import des bibliothques ncessaires
import yfinance as yf
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
from sklearn.preprocessing import MinMaxScaler
import datetime as dt
from sklearn.svm import SVR
from sklearn.metrics import mean_absolute_error
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from numpy import array

#Rcupration des donnes du DAX 40
df_SVR = yf.download("^GDAXI", start="2000-01-01", end="2022-12-31")
df_SVR = df_SVR[["Close"]]

#Normalizing / scaling close value between 0 to 1
Close_original = df_SVR.copy()
scaler=MinMaxScaler(feature_range=(0,1))
df_SVR=scaler.fit_transform(np.array(df_SVR).reshape(-1,1))
print(df_SVR.shape)

#Split train_test classique 70/30
training_size=int(len(df_SVR)*0.70)
test_size=len(df_SVR)-training_size
train_data,test_data=df_SVR[0:training_size,:],df_SVR[training_size:len(df_SVR),:1]
print("train_data: ", train_data.shape)
print("test_data: ", test_data.shape)

def creation_dataset(dataset, time_step=1):
    dataX = np.array([dataset[i:i+time_step, 0] for i in range(len(dataset)-time_step-1)])
    dataY = np.array([dataset[i+time_step, 0] for i in range(len(dataset)-time_step-1)])
    return dataX, dataY

#Reshape dataset
time_step = 100
X_train, y_train = creation_dataset(train_data, time_step)
X_test, y_test = creation_dataset(test_data, time_step)

print("X_train: ", X_train.shape)
print("y_train: ", y_train.shape)
print("X_test: ", X_test.shape)
print("y_test", y_test.shape)

#Super vector regression - SVR
svr_rbf = SVR(kernel= "linear", C= 1e2, gamma= 0.1)
svr_rbf.fit(X_train, y_train)

#Prdiction
train_predict=svr_rbf.predict(X_train)
test_predict=svr_rbf.predict(X_test)
    
train_predict = train_predict.reshape(-1,1)
test_predict = test_predict.reshape(-1,1)

print("Train data prediction:", train_predict.shape)
print("Test data prediction:", test_predict.shape)

#Scaler.inverse
train_predict = scaler.inverse_transform(train_predict)
test_predict = scaler.inverse_transform(test_predict)
original_ytrain = scaler.inverse_transform(y_train.reshape(-1,1)) 
original_ytest = scaler.inverse_transform(y_test.reshape(-1,1)) 

Train_data_MAE = mean_absolute_error(original_ytrain, train_predict)
Test_data_MAE = mean_absolute_error(original_ytest, test_predict)

print("Train data MAE: ", mean_absolute_error(original_ytrain,train_predict))
print("Test data MAE: ", mean_absolute_error(original_ytest,test_predict))

#Set-up plot prdiction train
look_back=time_step
Train_Prdiction_Plot = np.empty(shape=df_SVR.shape)
Train_Prdiction_Plot = np.full_like(df_SVR, np.nan)
Train_Prdiction_Plot[look_back:len(train_predict)+look_back, :] = train_predict
print("Train prdiction: ", Train_Prdiction_Plot.shape)

#Set-up plot prdiction test
Test_Prdiction_Plot = np.empty(shape=df_SVR.shape)
Test_Prdiction_Plot = np.full_like(df_SVR, np.nan)
Test_Prdiction_Plot[len(train_predict)+(look_back*2)+1:len(df_SVR)-1, :] = test_predict
print("Test prdiction: ", Test_Prdiction_Plot.shape)

#Cration du dataset pour le graphique
Close_original["Close"]
train_prd_close = Train_Prdiction_Plot.reshape(1,-1)[0].tolist()
test_prd_close = Test_Prdiction_Plot.reshape(1,-1)[0].tolist()
Plot_DF_SVR2 = pd.DataFrame({"Close": Close_original["Close"], "train_prdiction_close":train_prd_close, "test_prdiction_close": test_prd_close})

#Graphique
plt.figure(figsize=(18,10))
plt.style.use("seaborn")
plt.plot(Close_original.index, Plot_DF_SVR2["train_prdiction_close"], linewidth=1, color="red", alpha=1, label="Prdiction d'entrainement")
plt.plot(Plot_DF_SVR2.index, Plot_DF_SVR2["test_prdiction_close"], linewidth=1, color="blue", alpha=1, label="Prdiction de test")
plt.plot(Plot_DF_SVR2.index, Close_original["Close"], linewidth=1, color="green", alpha=0.8, label="DAX")
plt.title("Prdiction par Support Vector Regression (SVR)", fontsize=15, color="black")
plt.grid(True, which="both", linestyle="--", linewidth=0.5, color="gray")
_=plt.legend(loc="upper left")

#Predicting next 10 days
x_input=test_data[len(test_data)-time_step:].reshape(1,-1)
temp_input=list(x_input)
temp_input=temp_input[0].tolist()

lst_output=[]
n_steps=time_step
i=0
pred_days = 10
while(i<pred_days):
    
    if(len(temp_input)>time_step):
        
        x_input=np.array(temp_input[1:])
        x_input=x_input.reshape(1,-1)
        
        yhat = svr_rbf.predict(x_input)
        temp_input.extend(yhat.tolist())
        temp_input=temp_input[1:]
       
        lst_output.extend(yhat.tolist())
        i=i+1
        
    else:
        yhat = svr_rbf.predict(x_input)
        
        temp_input.extend(yhat.tolist())
        lst_output.extend(yhat.tolist())
        
        i=i+1
        
print("Output of predicted next days: ", len(lst_output))

#Plotting last 15 days and next predicted 10 days
last_days=np.arange(1,time_step+1)
day_pred=np.arange(time_step+1,time_step+pred_days+1)

temp_mat = np.empty((len(last_days)+pred_days+1,1))
temp_mat[:] = np.nan
temp_mat = temp_mat.reshape(1,-1).tolist()[0]

last_original_days_value = temp_mat
next_predicted_days_value = temp_mat

last_original_days_value[0:time_step+1] = scaler.inverse_transform(df_SVR[len(df_SVR)-time_step:]).reshape(1,-1).tolist()[0]
next_predicted_days_value[time_step+1:] = scaler.inverse_transform(np.array(lst_output).reshape(-1,1)).reshape(1,-1).tolist()[0]
Plot_DF_SVR2 = pd.DataFrame({"last_original_days_value":last_original_days_value,"next_predicted_days_value":next_predicted_days_value})

#Graphique
fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
plt.plot(Plot_DF_SVR2.index[100:], Plot_DF_SVR2["last_original_days_value"][100:], color="blue", label="Prdiction")
plt.plot(Plot_DF_SVR2.index[:100], Plot_DF_SVR2["next_predicted_days_value"][:100], color="green", label="Dax")
plt.title("100 derniers jours et la prdiction des 10 prochains jours (SVR)")
plt.legend(title="Prdiction des 10 prochains jours (SVR)")
plt.legend(loc="upper right")
plt.grid(True, which="both", linestyle="--", linewidth=0.5, color="gray")
